<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="/main.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Edu+NSW+ACT+Cursive:wght@400..700&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
   <style>
     * {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
}

body {
  background-color: #fff9af;
}

/* Heading */
.heading {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 20px;
  color: #fa812f;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* Main Section */
.main {
  width: 80%;
  height: auto;
  border: 2px solid #fa812f;
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 25px;
  margin: 25px auto;
  background-color: #fffdf5;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.main:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
}

/* Container: text + image */
.container {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 40px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

/* Image section */
.img_con img {
  width: 90%;
  max-width: 420px;
  height: auto;
  border-radius: 20px;
  margin-left: 20px;
  margin-top: 20px;
  box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.img_con img:hover {
  transform: scale(1.04);
}

/* Paragraph text */
.text p {
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: #333;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  text-align: justify;
}

/* Section Headings inside main */
.main h1 {
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-top: 25px;
  color: #3b38a0;
  border-left: 5px solid #fa812f;
  padding-left: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

/* List items */
.items {
  margin-left: 40px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-top: 15px;
  color: #444;
  font-size: 1rem;
}

.items li {
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 10px;
}

.items li::before {
  content: "✔";
  color: #fa812f;
  font-weight: bold;
  position: absolute;
  left: -20px;
}

/* Hover animation for list items */
.items li:hover {
  color: #3b38a0;
  transition: color 0.3s;
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .main {
    width: 90%;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .container {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .img_con img {
    width: 95%;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 0 10px;
  }

  .main h1 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .heading {
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .items {
    margin-left: 20px;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .heading {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
  }

  .text p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .main {
    padding: 15px;
  }

  .img_con img {
    max-width: 100%;
  }
}

   </style>
</head>
<body>
   <%- include("partial/nav")%>

    <h1 class="heading">Archery</h1>
    <div class="main">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text">
          <p> Archery – Immerse yourself in the thrilling world of archery, where precision meets patience and focus becomes
            your greatest ally. This activity challenges participants to hone their hand-eye coordination,
            concentration, and control, making every arrow a step toward personal growth. Under the guidance of
            skilled instructors in a safe and supportive environment, children and adults alike can experience the joy of aiming
             for the target, learning to adjust their techniques, and celebrating small victories with every successful shot.
             Beyond skill-building, archery fosters self-confidence,
           discipline, and a sense of achievement, all while providing an enjoyable, engaging, and memorable outdoor adventure.</p>
        </div>
         <div class="img_con">
             <img src="/pexels-ionatelo-27786385.jpg" alt="Archery image">
         </div>
    </div>
    <h1>Safety Precautions</h1>
       <ul class="items">
        <li>Check bows and arrows for damage before use.</li>
        <li>Keep a safe distance from others.</li>
        <li>Always shoot under instructor supervision.</li>
        <li>Maintain proper stance and shooting technique.</li>
       </ul>
     <h1>Requirements</h1>
       <ul class="items">
        <li>Bows</li>
        <li>Arrows</li>
        <li>Targets</li>
        <li>Finger Tabs or Gloves</li>
       </ul>

    </div>



</body>
</html>